Package: tidycreel.connect
Title: Database and File Connections for tidycreel
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Christopher", "Chizinski", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "chris.chizinski@unl.edu")
Description: Provides connection objects and data loaders for the tidycreel
    creel survey analysis package. Supports SQL Server (via ODBC),
    DBI-compliant databases, and flat CSV files.
